{
  "doc_id": "16537",
  "text": "Our aim is to gather preliminary assessment knowledge of a vaccine-centric CA to help refine our idea of utilizing an automated CA for HPV counseling at a clinical environment. For our early assessment and data collection process, we employed the Wizard of OZ protocol that simulates speech interfaces with a potential user who thinks they are interacting with an automated machine or robot [CITATION_1] . It allows us the evaluate the usability and acceptability of the system rather than to measure the quality of an entire system.",
